Definition.WordDefinition: Homemade \Home"made`\, a. Made at home; of domestic manufacture; made either in a private family or in one's own country. --Locke. [1913 Webster]
homemade adj : made or produced in the home or by yourself; "homemade bread" [ant: {factory-made}]
